WEBVTT

00:03:58.593 --> 00:04:01.362
Posredovali bodo v svojo okolico

00:04:01.386 --> 00:04:02.863
in rekli nekaj takega:

00:04:02.887 --> 00:04:04.271
"Torej, preverili smo.

00:04:04.295 --> 00:04:06.955
Smo na tej TEDx konferenci...

00:04:06.979 --> 00:04:09.909
(smeh)

00:04:11.083 --> 00:04:12.625
(aplavz)

00:04:13.378 --> 00:04:14.528
Plinasto?

00:04:14.552 --> 00:04:16.788
Mogoče, če sedite na strani

00:04:16.812 --> 00:04:20.201
in veste, da ga lahko spustite po tihem.

00:04:20.225 --> 00:04:22.065
(smeh)

00:04:22.089 --> 00:04:23.248
Ampak trdno...

00:04:23.272 --> 00:04:24.473
mogoče kasneje.

00:04:24.497 --> 00:04:25.940
(smeh)

00:04:25.964 --> 00:04:31.394
Ker so naša zapiralka in možgani
povezani z živčnimi celicami,